<Layout
  title="How to Create a Mobile App for Your Infosys Equinox Site"
  description="Learn how to seriously grow engagement, retention and revenue for your brand, by launching your own mobile app. MobiLoud makes converting your Infosys Equinox site into apps easy - learn more inside."
