      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to Create a Mobile App for Your Infosys Equinox Site</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Learn how to seriously grow engagement, retention and revenue for your brand, by launching your own mobile app. MobiLoud makes converting your Infosys Equinox site into apps easy - learn more inside.</p>
    </div>
